《'''In a Dream'''》是澳大利亚歌手[[特洛伊·希文|特洛伊·希文]]第五张EP, 于2020年8月21日通过 [[EMI_Music_Australia|EMI Music Australia]] 和[[Capitol_Records|Capitol Records]]发布. 这是他继第二张录音室专辑 ''[[Bloom_(Troye_Sivan_album)|Bloom]]'' (2018)后发布的专辑, 带有 "[[Take_Yourself_Home|Take Yourself Home]]", "[[Easy_(Troye_Sivan_song)|Easy]]" 和"[[Rager_Teenager!|Rager Teenager!]]"的特色.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/troye-sivan-announces-in-a-dream-ep-shares-new-song-easy-listen/|title=Troye Sivan Announces In a Dream EP, Shares New Song "Easy": Listen|website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]]|last=Moreland|first=Quinn|date=2020-07-15|accessdate=2020-07-17|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716073758/https://pitchfork.com/news/troye-sivan-announces-in-a-dream-ep-shares-new-song-easy-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Troye Sivan将"概念EP"描述为"一个仍在展开的故事”“这张小歌曲集探索了我人生中一个浪漫恰似“过山车”的时期，有着最令人震惊的情感和想法。当时的感觉和想法是最令人震惊的新奇。尽管重温这些歌曲和时刻是艰难的，但我为这首音乐感到骄傲，并很高兴能将它发布。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9418720/troye-sivan-announces-ep-easy|title=Troye Sivan Kicks Off ''In a Dream'' EP Rollout With Hypnotic New Single "Easy"|website=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|date=2020-07-15|accessdate=2020-07-18|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818212052/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9418720/troye-sivan-announces-ep-easy|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==发布和推广==
"[[Take_Yourself_Home|Take Yourself Home]]" 作为本张专辑的第一首歌曲于2020年4月1日在2019冠状病毒病疫情流行时异想天开的发布出来; 最初是由Lanning Sally执导的歌词MV，然后是在众多艺术家的帮助下制作的九种不同语言的歌词音乐錄影帶和“ Live From Home”音乐錄影帶。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Spanos|first=Brittany|date=2020-04-01|title=Troye Sivan Returns Earlier Than Planned With 'Take Yourself Home'|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/troye-sivan-take-yourself-home-new-song-975119/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213151927/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/troye-sivan-take-yourself-home-new-song-975119/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 专辑的第二首单曲, "[[Easy_(Troye_Sivan_song)|Easy]]", 在2020年7月15日发布，音乐錄影帶由Troye Sivan本人指导.<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-16|title=Troye Sivan Burns His Bridges (and Himself) in Melancholy 'Easy' Video: Watch|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9419536/troye-sivan-easy-video|access-date=2020-08-07|website=Billboard|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820061714/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9419536/troye-sivan-easy-video|dead-url=no}}</ref> 第三首单曲, "[[Rager_Teenager!|Rager Teenager!]]", 于2020年8月5日同由他本人自己指导的音乐錄影帶一同出人意料地发布.<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Troye Sivan Pays Homage to His Wild Child With Surprise Single 'Rager Teenager'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9429643/troye-sivan-rager-teenager-video|access-date=2020-08-07|website=Billboard|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020033704/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/9429643/troye-sivan-rager-teenager-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>

